  Locus:
    Page: 275
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Journey
---
We think we must climb to a certain height of goodness before we can reach
God. But He says not, “At the end of the way you may find me.” He says, “I
am the Way; I am the road under your feet, the road that begins just as low
down as you happen to be.”
